# Workspace rules

Authoritative project guidance (TypeScript stack, BDD workflow, commit format, branching, feature catalog) lives in **`docs/tech.md`**. Read and follow that file; do not restate it here in different words.

## Keeping docs and rules aligned

- When you change tooling, workflow, or the feature catalog, **update `docs/tech.md`**.
- If `.cursor/rules` needs a Cursor-only note (see below), add or edit it in the same change so expectations stay consistent.

## Cursor-specific

- Communicate concisely in chat; clarity beats perfect grammar.
